          <label-location>
            <id type="integer">1096177</id>
            <visualization-template-id type="integer">15</visualization-template-id>
            <label-text>Tafluprost activates prostaglandin EP3 receptor which activates the Gi protein signaling cascade.</label-text>
            <x type="integer">1388</x>
            <y type="integer">365</y>
            <zindex type="integer">20</zindex>
            <scale-x type="decimal">3.1</scale-x>
            <scale-y type="decimal">3.1</scale-y>
            <width>160</width>
            <height>15</height>
          </label-location>
          <label-location>
            <id type="integer">1096178</id>
            <visualization-template-id type="integer">15</visualization-template-id>
            <label-text>Adenylate cyclase is inhibited therefore, cAMP production is reduced.</label-text>
            <x type="integer">1378</x>
            <y type="integer">745</y>
            <zindex type="integer">20</zindex>
            <scale-x type="decimal">2.8</scale-x>
            <scale-y type="decimal">2.8</scale-y>
            <width>160</width>
            <height>15</height>
          </label-location>
          <label-location>
            <id type="integer">1096179</id>
            <visualization-template-id type="integer">15</visualization-template-id>
            <label-text>cAMP activates protein kinase A, which activates the proton pump.</label-text>
            <x type="integer">1553</x>
            <y type="integer">1478</y>
            <zindex type="integer">20</zindex>
            <scale-x type="decimal">2.5</scale-x>
            <scale-y type="decimal">2.5</scale-y>
            <width>160</width>
            <height>15</height>
          </label-location>
          <label-location>
            <id type="integer">1096180</id>
            <visualization-template-id type="integer">15</visualization-template-id>
            <label-text> Low cAMP concentration, results in less activated protein kinase A, therefore activation of the proton pump is reduced and less acid (H+) is pumped into the stomach lumen, reducing acidity.</label-text>
            <x type="integer">1903</x>
            <y type="integer">2056</y>
            <zindex type="integer">20</zindex>
            <scale-x type="decimal">2.5</scale-x>
            <scale-y type="decimal">2.5</scale-y>
